title: One Bedroom Now Available @ $1853 @ Arbor Terraces Senior Apts
posting_body: ['2760 McKee Road, San Jose, CA 95127', 'show contact info', 'FEATURES', 'Bedrooms: 1', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Floors in Bldg: 3', 'Square Footage: 556', 'Pets Allowed: None', 'Year Built: 1999', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Centrally located close to freeways, public transportation, a range of medical facilities, fine neighborhood shopping centers, and outstanding local restaurants, Arbor Terraces Senior Apartments is a beautiful affordable housing community that offers its residents the opportunity to enjoy good times with the company of a community of friends and a beautiful, maintenance free, spacious apartment.', 'Our charming one bedroom one bath units have fully equipped kitchens, ample closet space, window treatments, and an abundance of space awaiting your personal interior touch.', 'Meeting new people and engaging in conversation with friends is always a possibility at Arbor Terraces Senior Apartments with its many attractive lounges throughout the property, welcoming Courtyards, and fully furnished Community Room.', 'Arbor Terraces also offers its residents centrally located Elevators, a fully-equipped Fitness Center, and a Computer Room with Internet access.', "Monthly professionally planned community activities, outings, and social events allow Arbor Terraces residents' the opportunity to meet neighbors and friends that share the same interest and hobbies.", 'If Arbor Terraces offers what you are looking for, please consider this our personal invitation to discover the atmosphere of our community for yourself.', 'Schedule a tour today!', 'Section 8 Vouchers accepted', '**Income Restrictions Apply**', 'Visit us at <URL>', 'RENTAL UNIT AMENITIES', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Patio', 'Balcony', 'Wall A/C', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', 'On-site Laundry', 'On-site Manager', 'Clubhouse', 'Exercise Room', 'Security Gate', 'Community Room', 'Computer Room', 'OTHER PRICING DETAILS', "Deposit: one month's rent", 'Minimum Lease: 1 year']
